1、服务器配置（php.ini）
post_max_size=8M
upload_max_filesize=20M

2、数据库配置（configs.php）
define("DB_HOST", "localhost");
define("DB_USER", "root");
define("DB_PWD", "");
define("DB_DBNAME","yandingtech");
define("DB_CHARSET", "utf-8");

3、上传图片配置（upload_json.php）
$water_img = $_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] .'/yanding/images/logo1.png';